{"tid":337924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：$1500力王筍工　200kg日搬15次","createTime":"2017-07-27T17:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T15:20:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f58a221f63fef0381bb43d1351e721681a935a9","tid":337924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170727/photo/bkn-20170727114329590-0727_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170727141632\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170727%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170727114329590-0727_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170727141632&h=d1e3079b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有請力王出場！最近社交網站Facebook「Tai Po 大埔」群組，有網民轉載「運輸界朋友互掟Order」群組一個貼文，招聘一名跟車，需要識搬運及熟悉唧車，朝8半晚6，做完收工， 1500港元日薪，看似筍工。但仔細一看，要雙手搬起一桶220kg桶，合共有15桶，轉載網民對於要搬咁重的桶感到「滴汗」，更留言詢問「有無力王需要搵工」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民紛紛留言指招聘貼文「玩野(嘢)」，又稱「無可能請到，世界記(紀)錄保持者先做到OVER200...」；有網民笑言「雙手搬起220kg=484磅，可參加亞運」。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說:<br />\n<br />\nYi Wah Li：單手點計？做完收工？緊係收工啦，以後番唔到工tim(添)，即出？出殯<br />\n<br />\nDeric Tse：試解畫：要搬既(嘅)係咪220kg size既(嘅)吉桶咋？<br />\n<br />\nPoon Wai Yip：收1500一日，但返完每日放工後看醫生要3000<br />\n<br />\nMarco Lee：x，變形俠醫呀？480磅呀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170727/bkn-20170727114329590-0727_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170727%2Fbkn-20170727114329590-0727_00822_001.html&d=5f8aTq4Pbr%2B9gATaFqyk6JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=93e9f1f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170727/bkn-20170727114329590-0727_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bc0efa3e6d13028e7d64d58aab5094ca9c76147b","tid":337924,"uid":98386,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"兩個人都搬唔郁啦戇尻 唔好話千五 萬五都冇人做 因為根本做唔黎"},{"pid":"63a0b6d02a23f2c24f3cf653a6054f151fc22ea8","tid":337924,"uid":5649,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:43:29.000Z","