製衣<br />\n個單位係點我又真係唔知<br />\n今晚返去問下</blockquote><br />\n咪問啦，你老豆想威吹大自己能力之嘛，再問落去想佢點兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用膊頭上貨唔係用手搬係唔同. 200斤係真係得<br />\n<br />\n利申: 細路仔嗰時幫老豆手, 親眼見到老豆用膊頭上200斤貨去三樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯 上膊可以承受你體重一倍重量既野 所以理論同實踐上都可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860491cd9c73fc1affe2f1582fb4c3c7110b17e7","tid":337924,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"咁陰力既話可以會舉到"},{"pid":"be79ea6fd69b96dd0453383d16c6a4e9a5ccfae0","tid":337924,"uid":99397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雪櫃點樣上膊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想學嘢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jkqwhby7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjkqwhby7&h=4a8c92a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/144453_894a087dedfe45c138018fbe2571579f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F144453_894a087dedfe45c138018fbe2571579f.jpg&h=9f665577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踏埋單車都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5e7e09df94009e744f949304a2eb6a4f5b1c83","tid":337924,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"留意到而家d連登囝真係好weak<br />\n以前d高登仔單手都抬起個集裝箱"},{"pid":"84efbe61373437b9d7235e8e79f234100e498185","tid":337924,"uid":445,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留意到而家d連登囝真係好weak<br />\n以前d高登仔單手都抬起個集裝箱</blockquote><br 