me":"2017-07-28T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌d細蚊仔咪走過黎吹水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩雪櫃可以一個人上樓梯啊</blockquote><br />\n你咪細蚊仔囉<br />\n<br />\n綁繩咩仔咪上到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0499a1aa35f7827f54251806239a476b4985bf6","tid":337924,"uid":36116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌d細蚊仔咪走過黎吹水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩雪櫃可以一個人上樓梯啊</blockquote><br />\n屌，你搬過屋未呀？定係你搵個間搬屋公司既人廢呀？我搬過2次，大大個雪櫃都係一條友，加一條布帶就背上背脊度上樓！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，電梯上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未見過當冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6965487300d80cb682c1c1b0bbe56d7158b11c7e","tid":337924,"uid":5713,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/10-20-2015/1w7huI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F10-20-2015%2F1w7huI.gif&h=465fc798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好玩啦 200kg 好輕姐<br />\n香港人好犀利架 平時日常你同我都會拎既野<br />\n奥運選手都拎唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea205e8629909054d4d6484993bdd78eed002c6","tid":337924,"uid":130246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>On撚鳩<br />\n220kg<br />\n奧運都做唔到啦<br />\n唔係挺舉<br />\n而係拎住行<br />\n痴線</blockquote><br />\n其實只要個桶有柄位可以出力其實都勉力可以搬到<br />\n如果乜都無一個圓桶就真係無方法了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難。</blockquote><br />\n金輪法王表示我一拳都一千斤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岳飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未冠，能挽弓三百斤</blockquote><br />\n挽你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪無文化架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e861312cd5f0fb714f1c0d6cf2ac3140541efe","tid":337924,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d2e37be4bfbd9850e13fca16e3a51dc1db7160e","tid":337924,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c28a9639b8a8cd01e099c0e9bfe805e622f10d74","tid":337924,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"你地知唔知最難搬係咩？ <br />\n<br />\n我以前做過影印機， 唔係好重， 我估都係百幾磅， 兩個人搬本來都唔係太辛苦。 但係影印機有樣仆街野， 就係唔可以打側， 如果唔係D碳粉會倒晒出黎。 平路都唔係問題， 上樓梯就仆街囉 ！！ 一前一後， 一個要彎腰差唔多90度兜住， 另一個要舉到上心口。吊你老母真係上幾級就要抖一抖。 上2層樓真係命都無。"},{"pid":"7b1dad57c778327ffb09a2ce85e91c3a864569dd","tid":337924,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地知唔知最難搬係咩？ <br />\n<br />\n我以前做過影印機， 唔係好重， 我估都係百幾磅， 兩個人搬本來都唔係太辛苦。 但係影印機有樣仆街野， 就係唔可以打側， 如果唔係D碳粉會倒晒出黎。 平路都唔係問題， 上樓梯就仆街囉 ！！ 一前一後， 一個要彎腰差唔多90度兜住， 另一個要舉到上心口。吊你老母真係上幾級就要抖一抖。 上2層樓真係命都無。</blockquote><br />\n咁一開始倒晒出黎再搬完倒返入去?"},{"pid":"2ff0d4f4ffa60637fffde45b7180911a18397604","tid":337924,"uid":230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"打側個筒轆渣嘛？"},{"pid":"a242a7356b4a298711d67ee53debd891c0b40c08","tid":337924,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On撚鳩<br />\n220kg<br />\n奧運都做唔到啦<br />\n唔係挺舉<br />\n而係拎住行<br />\n痴線</blockquote><br />\n其實只要個桶有柄位可以出力其實都勉力可以搬到<br />\n如果乜都無一個圓桶就真係無方法了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e67