:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌d細蚊仔咪走過黎吹水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩雪櫃可以一個人上樓梯啊</blockquote><br />\n屌，你搬過屋未呀？定係你搵個間搬屋公司既人廢呀？我搬過2次，大大個雪櫃都係一條友，加一條布帶就背上背脊度上樓！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，電梯上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未見過當冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左，細蚊仔笑鳩人細蚊仔"},{"pid":"18f7f9f4b68cb24d4bd3fe66821c5bdbd20ff49c","tid":337924,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"023ca9575717a1a0cf1ed92045eeb458d94926ab","tid":337924,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n吹水既野， 你唔係信呀嘛<br />\n200 磅都攞你命啦， 斤。</blockquote><br />\n200斤成 4百幾磅，起碼有個半個欣宣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1斤（香港）= 0.61公斤<br />\n即係122kg</blockquote><br />\n1 : 0.61 呢個係台灣斤<br />\n大陸斤係 1 : 0.5<br />\n<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n果陣佢係香港做製衣<br />\n個單位係點我又真係唔知<br />\n今晚返去問下</blockquote><br />\n咪問啦，你老豆想威吹大自己能力之嘛，再問落去想佢點兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用膊頭上貨唔係用手搬係唔同. 200斤係真係得<br />\n<br />\n利申: 細路仔嗰時幫老豆手, 親眼見到老豆用膊頭上200斤貨去三樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯 上膊可以承受你體重一倍重量既野 所以理論同實踐上都可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔係上膊<br />\n佢係用背脊揹住上"}]}